member.name: PSS_AUXILIARY_PAGE_ENTRY
member.summary: Holds auxiliary page entry information returned by PssWalkSnapshot.

member.name: PSS_AUXILIARY_PAGE_ENTRY.Address
member.summary: The address of the captured auxiliary page, in the context of the captured process.

member.name: PSS_AUXILIARY_PAGE_ENTRY.BasicInformation
member.summary: Basic information about the captured page. See for more information.

member.name: PSS_AUXILIARY_PAGE_ENTRY.CaptureTime
member.summary: The capture time of the page. For more information, see .

member.name: PSS_AUXILIARY_PAGE_ENTRY.PageContents
member.summary: A pointer to the contents of the captured page, in the context of the current process. This member may be NULL if page contents were not captured. The pointer is valid for the lifetime of the walk marker passed to PssWalkSnapshot.

member.name: PSS_AUXILIARY_PAGE_ENTRY.PageSize
member.summary: The size of the page contents that PageContents points to, in bytes.
